==Introduction==
The '''Time Property Type''' represents a date and time values.

The Wiki Automation Tool supports editing, viewing and searching on the DateTime properties.


==Definition==
The Time Type doesn't define any additional configuration attributes in the  [[Help:Property|Property Definition]] section.


==Semantic database==
The Time Property is implemented as a [[Special:Types/Text]] MediaWiki datatype.


==Example==
<pre>
<property name="Start time" type="Time" label="Start time" attribute="starttime">
  <description>A date and time to start an event in a concept.</description>
  <instruction/>
</property>
</pre>


==User Interface==
* '''View Page'''
The property displays a date and time value.

* '''Edit Page'''
The property provides a Time Picker input field.

* '''Search Page'''
The property allows user to choose a search operator from the following options: ''After (exc), After (inc), Before (exc), Before (inc), Equals (day), Has any value''
and allows user to enter a desired date using DateTime Picker input field.
